    "title": "Vacancy for Category Manager at Grofers Advisory Limited",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Grofers Advisory Limited. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Category Manager to strengthen our Jaipur-based team.\n\nAbout Grofers Advisory Limited:\nGrofers Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Shopify\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in SEO/SEM\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Learning & development budget\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Referral bonus program\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jaipur, Rajasthan, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Grofers Advisory Limited!",
